Task: KwAnRB-x-refactor
==============================================================================

Motivation
----------

The x.py tool 2614 lines long, which is longer than we would like in other for
the file to be easily maintained.

Goals
--------

This tasks is to refactor x.py into a number of separate modules in order to
ease maintainance and provide a structure on which future features can be added.

Test Plan
---------

 * All existing tests on TeamCity will continue to pass
 * pylint will be used to capture possible errors in un-tested branches of the code

